---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/PageHero.astro";

// Service delivery / fulfilment policy for card purchases.
const updated = "21 July 2026";
---

<BaseLayout
  current="pricing"
  title="Service Delivery Policy — Coworking Prilep"
  description="How and when Coworking Prilep delivers the services you buy online: confirmation, access, and timing."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Legal"
    title="Delivery Policy"
    subtitle="How and when we deliver the services you buy online: your confirmation, your access, and the timing."
  />

  <article class="px-6 pb-24 md:px-12 md:pb-32">
    <div class="prose-cws mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <p class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.25em] text-bone/40 uppercase">
        Last updated: {updated}
      </p>

      <h2>1. What we deliver</h2>
      <p>
        Coworking Prilep, operated by <strong>Dastian DOO Prilep</strong>, sells
        <strong>services</strong> — access to our shared workspace and its
        facilities (dedicated desks, hot desks, meeting room, classroom, and
        related amenities). These are provided at our premises in Prilep, North
        Macedonia, and there is normally no physical item to ship.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Confirmation of your purchase</h2>
      <p>
        As soon as your card payment is approved, we send a
        <strong>confirmation email with your payment receipt</strong> to the
        address you provided, usually within a few minutes. This email is your
        proof of purchase and sets out what you bought and the amount paid. An
        invoice is issued as described in section 5.
      </p>

      <h2>3. When your service becomes available</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Memberships</strong> become active on the start date shown at
          checkout (immediately, or on a date you choose). Access details are
          included in your confirmation or provided at the space.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Passes and hour credits</strong> are available to use straight
          away, within their stated validity period.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Meeting room and classroom bookings</strong> are reserved for the
          specific date and time you select and confirmed by email.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. If you don't receive your confirmation</h2>
      <p>
        If you don't get a confirmation email within a few minutes, please check
        your spam folder, then contact us at
        <a href="mailto:coworkingprilep@outlook.com">coworkingprilep@outlook.com</a>.
        We'll confirm your purchase and resend it. Do not attempt the payment again
        before checking with us, to avoid a duplicate charge (which we would refund
        under our <a href="/refunds">Refund Policy</a>).
      </p>

      <h2>5. Invoices</h2>
      <p>
        An invoice for your purchase is available on request and, where required, is
        sent to your email. If you need an invoice with company (B2B) details,
        include your company name, address, and tax number (ЕДБ) when you buy or by
        email afterwards.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Physical items</h2>
      <p>
        If we ever sell or send a physical item (for example, a welcome package or
        merchandise), we will hand it over at the space or deliver it within North
        Macedonia within <strong>5 business days</strong>, and the specific terms
        will be shown at the time of purchase.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Dastian DOO Prilep, Kej 1-vi Maj no. 9, Prilep, North Macedonia ·
        <a href="mailto:coworkingprilep@outlook.com">coworkingprilep@outlook.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
